priority-pdx-sip-stay\",\"description\":\"Slabtown taproom with retractable walls, hazy IPAs, and staff monitors so you can host brewery playdates rain or...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Portland\",\"addressRegion\":\"OR\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508672019048-805c876b67e2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80\"}},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"item\":{\"@type\":\"SportsActivityLocation\",\"@id\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/priority-pdx-eastbank\",\"name\":\"Eastbank Enrichment Collective\",\"url\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/parks/priority-pdx-eastbank\",\"description\":\"Buckman studio built for agility teams—think rubber flooring, scent work labs, and livestream-ready lighting for...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Portland\",\"addressRegion\":\"OR\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"image\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1477973770766-6228305816df?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where can I walk my dog indoors in Portland?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Our directory currently lists 4 indoor dog parks in Portland. Use the “Indoor Dog Park” filter on this page to jump straight to climate-controlled options.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How much do Portland indoor dog parks cost?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Expect $18–$25 drop-ins that include a pint or coffee credit, plus $110–$150 monthly memberships that unlock event rentals and late-night rain plans.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do memberships include brewery or event perks?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes—many Portland operators partner with craft beverage clubs so you can earn bar tabs, reserve private taproom yards, o