class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Interactive planning</span><h2>See everything laid out on the map</h2><p>Use the live map to lock in nearby options, preview ratings, and save time hopping between neighborhoods.</p></div><div class=\"map-grid\"><div class=\"map-panel\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><div style=\"min-height:320px;background:#f3f4f6\"></div><!--/$--></div><div class=\"map-sidebar\"><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Quick filters</h3><div class=\"map-chip-grid\"><button type=\"button\"><span>Indoor Dog Park</span><small>4</small></button></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card\"><h3>Highest-rated nearby</h3><div class=\"mini-park-list\"><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Pearl Pack Pavilion</p><span>Indoor Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.8</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Rain City Rovers</p><span>Indoor Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.7</strong></div><div class=\"mini-park-card\"><div><p>Sip &amp; Stay Yard</p><span>Indoor Dog Park</span></div><strong>4.6</strong></div></div></div><div class=\"map-sidebar-card muted\"><p>Plot a loop: Pearl for polished rentals, Slabtown for breweries, and Central Eastside for agility labs.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"planning-essentials\" class=\"planning-essentials-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Visit toolkit</span><h2>Plan the perfect dog outing in <!-- -->Portland</h2><p>Borrow best practices from local trainers, rangers, and experienced pet parents.</p></div><div class=\"planning-grid\"><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-cloud-rain\"></i></div><h3>Rain plan essentials</h3><ul><li>Reserve in advance on stormy weekends</li><li>Pack quick-dry towels + slip-proof shoes</li><li>Use onsite dryers before heading back to the car</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-emoji-smile\"></i></div><h3>Social hour</h3><ul><li>Arrive early for beverage service</li><li>Respect brewery dog rules (no table paws)</li><li>Tip bar + cleanup teams—they flip spaces fast</li></ul></article><article class=\"planning-card\"><div class=\"planning-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-building\"></i></div><h3>Event rentals</h3><ul><li>Submit permit requests 3 weeks out</li><li>Coordinate with preferred caterers</li><li>Add donation drives for rescue partners</li></ul></article></div></div></section><section id=\"owner-cta\" class=\"owner-cta-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Partner with us</span><h2>Feature your Portland dog park</h2><p>Upgrade to a featured listing, share live availability, or pitch a new indoor concept. Our team drives qualified local pet parents every week.</p><div class=\"hero-cta-row\" style=\"margin-top:24px\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">List a property</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Contact the team</a></div></div></section><section id=\"park-directory\" class=\"park-directory-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">City directory</span><h2>All dog parks in <!-- -->Portland</h2><p>Filter-ready cards with ratings, amenities, and quick actions. Use the chips to jump between sections.</p></div><div class=\"category-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\">Indoor Dog Park</button></div><div id=\"indoor-dog-park-parks\" class=\"directory-category\"><div class=\"directory-header\"><div><h3>Indoor Dog Park<!-- -->s<!-- --> in <!-- -->Portland</h3><p>4<!-- --> locations ·<!-- --> <!-- -->4.7<!-- --> <!-- -->average rating</p></div><span class=\"directory-count\">4</span></div><div class=\"directory-grid\"><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/priority-pdx-rain-city\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Rain City Rovers</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Portland<!-- -->, <!-- -->OR</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"><span class=\"premium-badge type-badge\">INDOOR</span><span class=\"premium-badge price-badge\">$$</span></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Central Eastside warehouse strung with skylights, kombucha taps, and rentable event pods so rainy afternoons still feel celebratory.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/priority-pdx-sip-stay\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Sip &amp; Stay Yard</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Portland<!-- -->, <!-- -->OR</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"><span class=\"premium-badge type-badge\">INDOOR</span><span class=\"premium-badge price-badge\">$$</span></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Slabtown taproom with retractable walls, hazy IPAs, and staff monitors so you can host brewery playdates rain or shine.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/priority-pdx-pearl-pack\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Pearl Pack Pavilion</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Portland<!-- -->, <!-- -->OR</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"><span class=\"premium-badge type-badge\">INDOOR</span><span class=\"premium-badge price-badge\">$$$</span></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Pearl District pavilion with gallery lighting, rentable stages, and partnerships with local chefs for brunch pop-ups.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/priority-pdx-eastbank\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Eastbank Enrichment Collective</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Portland<!-- -->, <!-- -->OR</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"><span class=\"premium-badge type-badge\">INDOOR</span><span class=\"premium-badge price-badge\">$$</span></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Buckman studio built for agility teams—think rubber flooring, scent work labs, and livestream-ready lighting for competitions.</p></div></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"faq-section\" class=\"city-faq-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"faq-section\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-section\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-shell\"><div aria-labelledby=\"faq-heading\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-header\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a section-eyebrow\">Helpful Information</span><h2 id=\"faq-heading\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Frequently asked questions about <!-- -->Portland<!-- --> dog parks</h2><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Real-world guidance covering pricing, safety, etiquette, and planning for more than <!-- -->4<!-- --